# 🎯 Today's Goal

By the end of today, your app will:

* ✅ Show whether the selected file is a PDF or an Image.
* ✅ Display a different icon based on the file type.
* ✅ Show a green success message after selecting a file.
* ✅ Allow the user to remove the selected file.
* ✅ Prevent uploading if no file is selected.

This is exactly how many real apps behave before uploading a file.

